Leah: That's right. The Rune Academy holds it every semester. Everyone has a great time~
Leah: Even though Atlas has gotten warmer, the waterways haven't completely thawed out. There are huge ice patches all over the place.
Leah: All we need is to use a rune device to heat up the ice blocks and make 'em melt. Spend a little bit of time and we can make a swimming hole...
Lio: Ah, then we can play in the water!
Leah: Uh-huh. That'll raise everyone's spirits for sure~
Nigel: ...Leah, everyone is busy with the reconstruction. There's no need to get distracted with boring stuff like that.
Leah: But it's precisely 'cuz everyone is so strained that they need to relax a bit!
Nigel: And what if everyone gets too relaxed, what then?
Nigel: Those bandits aren't small in number. We don't know when they're gonna attack...
Fredrica: You're too stiff, horn boy~
Fredrica: Bunny-boo, I like what you've got going on.
Fredrica: That's a great idea~
Leah: Ｗell, only someone as amazing as you could get it done~
Fredrica: Such a sweet-talker...okay, I'll help out.
Fredrica: Horn boy, we brought all the supplies, all you need to do is set up a small site.
Fredrica: This will be a perfect, refreshing fair~
Jerome: Wait, wait, wait, General Lucien. The supplies the queen sent aren't to be used in this way...
Fredrica: What's it matter? I mean, we did bring it to 'em. We must make sure there's nothing wrong with the stuff~
Leah: Fredrica's right, we're just doing what's right~
Nigel: Quit making decisions without thinking things over!
Nigel: I haven't agreed to hold a fair──
Yamitsuki: ...A fair?
Nigel: Yamitsuki, why are you here?
Yamitsuki: The western patrol is complete. Found no tracks of the enemy. The eastern front still hasn't been checked, right? I'll get right to it.
Nigel: N-No...I just returned from there.
Nigel: These are emissaries of the queen. They just helped beat back the bandits. No need to worry for the time being.
Leah: Eve!!
Yamitsuki: ...Leah, long time no see.
Leah: Ya!! Hey, we need your help with something.
Yamitsuki: Help?
Leah: Fredrica, whatta you think of this young lady?
Fredrica: .........
Fredrica: ...Let me take care of her.
Jerome: General! When did you bring all that...
Fredrica: There were too many outfits. I wanted to make my decision on the road...
Fredrica: Luckily, now everyone gets to pick the one they want~
Yamitsuki: Leah, what the hell...
Leah: Sis, this is to help recover everyone's energy~
Leah: You're definitely willing to help, right?
Yamitsuki: If that's the case...of course.
Leah: Wonderful!
Yamitsuki: Ah...why do I have to take it off?
Fredrica: Young woman, don't think about it~we'll take care of this.
Leah: Wah, Eve's got such a nice body~
Fredrica: Okay, finished!
Yamitsuki: This outfit...ah!
Yamitsuki: There's barely anything...but it's really easy to move in.
Fredrica: Perfect! Horny boy, you like?
Nigel: ...I...it's...um...
Leah: Com' on, what a rare opportunity. Everyone put on a swimsuit!
Leah: This'll be an awesome fair~
Nigel: W-Wait, we've never held this type of event. Not everyone will want to attend...
Fredrica: Don't worry, as long as someone gets the party started, everyone will jump onboard. For example...
Fredrica: ...Miss Yamitsuki, take two steps, will you?
Yamitsuki: ...Like this?
Fredrica: Stop! Too ordinary. There's no UMPH in there!
Yamitsuki: Um...
Fredrica: Listen, you've got a perfect figure, if you don't use it, it'd be such a waste.
Fredrica: Com' on. A wider a range, a bit sexier...
Fredrica: Like this~That's the key.
Yamitsuki: ...I'll do my best.
Yamitsuki: Sorry...I don't think I did it too well.
Fredrica: No, no, no. This young, inexperienced feel is precisely what's important. Just make some minor adjustments and you'll drive all the men crazy~
Leah: She's right, you can definitely do it, Eve...
Lio: Eh? Nigel, your face is red.
Nigel: W-W-What? No, I...
Izumi: ...*sigh*...Nigel, you've got a fever~Must be 'cuz the air isn't circulating well~
Nigel: You little...what do you want?
Izumi: Heehee, let's talk in private.
Izumi: Let me borrow him, little bun-bun~
Lio: ...Little bun-bun?
Nigel: What are you doing, getting me alone? You want to discuss our "plan"?
Izumi: Ahahaha, too serious~don't worry about them.
Izumi: Our little Nigel has his own ideas~
Nigel: Hmph. You feeling me out?
Nigel: There's no way Angel turned virtuous all of a sudden, sending food. She must be taking this opportunity to learn about the situation in Atlas.
Nigel: Best hide this...I won't let just anyone know about it.
Izumi: Heehee...that puts me at ease.
Izumi: However, that's not what I came here for.
Nigel: ...Well then?
Izumi: Stunned, were you? Yamitsuki just now.
Nigel: S-Stunned?
Izumi: Ahahaha, don't play dumb! I know what's going on. You haven't stopped staring at her~
Nigel: Th-That's because she's been overworked recently. I'm just worried about her...
Izumi: Oh? A face that red, doesn't look like you're just "worried"...
Nigel: Cut it out or I'll teach you a lesson!
Izumi: Aigh-ya, just admit it~
Izumi: You don't want anyone else to see Yamitsuki like that...
Izumi: No, no, what I meant was "your Yamitsuki"...
Nigel: N-No, NO, AAAARGHH!!!!!!
Lio: WAH! What are you two doing?
Yamitsuki: Nigel, what happened?
Nigel: Um...
Izumi: Ah~nothing, nothing Yamitsuki.
Izumi: It's all Nigel's fault. He doesn't want to hold this fair, so he started arguing with me.
Lio: Ah, you like fairs too?
Izumi: Of course~How could I miss something this interesting?
Izumi: Everyone will definitely be looking forward to it!
Yamitsuki: Nigel, I know you're worried about the bandits, but everyone has been too strained. They can't take it anymore.
Yamitsuki: I don't know what this fair is, but if it really can help everyone relax...
Nigel: You...you won't be upset?
Yamitsuki: ...Upset?
Nigel: Uh, nothing...if you're okay, that's all that matters.
Nigel: ...*cough*...well, since Yamitsuki feels this way...
Nigel: ...Well, let's hold this "fair" thing.
Lio: Wonderful, Nigel!
Leah: Quick, head back and tell Fredrica the good news~
Nigel: Wait, no pushing...
Izumi: Hmph, a fair? Interesting...
Izumi: Looks like I've got a chance to show everyone what I've got~
